code: selflatex = function(src_file,dest_file,callback){    // split with src file name     var texname = src_file.split('/').splice(-1)[0].split('.')[0];    // compile and     exec(\"pdflatex -output-directory \" + dest_file + \" \" + src_file, (err,stdout,stderr) => {        if (err) {            callback(1,`pdflatex[1] error: ${err}`);        }else{            // compile second time to fit the usage            exec(\"pdflatex -output-directory \" + dest_file + \" \" + src_file, (err,stdout,stderr) => {                if (err) {                    callback(1,`pdflatex[2] error: ${err}`);                }                else{                    callback(0,`[node-latex-complete] Complete source: ${src_file}, check out result in ${dest_file}!`);                }            });        }    });}
